## Objective
Remove horizontal scroll from the gifts list page.

Current: Has scroll wrapper from previous fix (flex-1 overflow-hidden + inner overflow-y), but perhaps outer Container or html has overflow-x visible, or the gift cards with borders/shadows or the zoom overlay or script causes layout shift/width. Or the header + list in max-w-lg but with body margins/paddings or safe areas causing h-scroll on certain devices.

Fix: Ensure no element exceeds viewport width. Add overflow-x-hidden to html/body or specific containers if needed. Check card styles, the .gift-btn etc. Make sure the shelf doesn't cause h-scroll. Preserve vertical scroll for list.

## Constraints / Invariants
- Keep the new top-first reverse and vertical list scroll.
- IIPS, preserve animations (pulse-border, zoom).
- No impact on other pages.
- Verify with build + mental mobile.

## Verification
- No horizontal scrollbar on gifts page (desktop/mobile sim).
- List still scrolls vertically, cards stack nicely.
- Build clean, no layout breakage.
